   PASSION-FILM-REVIEW (Undated) _ ``Passion of Mind'': Alain
Berliner, director; with Demi Moore, Stellan Skarsgard, William
Fichtner, Sinead Cusak, Peter Riegert. Reviewed by Elvis Mitchell.
</P>
<P>
   NOON-FILM-REVIEW (Undated) _ ``Shanghai Noon'': Tom Dey,
director; with Jackie Chan, Lucy Liu, Owen Wilson. Reviewed by A.O.
Scott.
</P>
<P>
   CHAIR-BOOK-REVIEW (Undated) _ ``The Binding Chair,'' by Kathryn
Harrison (Random House). Reviewed by Michiko Kakutani.
</P>
<P>
   TV-WEEKEND (Undated) _ Caryn James spotlights the weekend's
television fare: Saturday on Showtime: ``Dirty Pictures.''
</P>
