<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-26 11:16 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6333 &Cx1f; tad-z
u w BC-CHINA-STUDENTS-0527-C     05-26 0941
