   SOWING DISSENT
</P>
<P>
   GMO-SEEDS-CONTAMINATE-NONGMOS-NEW-SCIENTIST-NYTSF &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   According to an American company, the latest furor over
accidental planting of genetically modified seed in Europe may be
the tip of the iceberg. Genetic ID told New Scientist that more
than half of 20 random samples of United States seed distributors
contained detectable traces of GM seed.
</P>
<P>
   BEHIND THE MAGIC
</P>
<P>
   VACCINE-EFFICACY-MYSTERY-NEW-SCIENTIST-NYTSF &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Basic ignorance about how vaccines like polio and measles
actually work is stalling the urgent quest for an AIDS vaccine, say
leading HIV researchers. The assumption that successful vaccines
work by simply producing antibodies is almost certainly wrong.
</P>
<P>
   NEW WATCH FOR DIABETICS MEASURES GLUCOSE LEVELS
</P>
<P>
   DIABETICS-WATCH-MEASURES-BLOOD-SUGAR-NEW-SCIENTIST-NYTSF &LR;  &QL;
</P>
