<P>
   NY-NIGHTLIFE (New York) _ If you're the kind of person who likes
to meditate to Run DMC, is there a club for you! It's Spa, a
cavernous new dance space in the East Village, which has boldly
attempted to graft a New Age ethos _ waterfalls! plants! _ with a
sound system so loud it makes your teeth chatter. Such are the
surreal sights encountered during a recent sojourn on the nightlife
circuit, those mystical grounds behind the velvet ropes where club
owners are constantly juggling all manner of concepts and looks to
try to satisfy the city's famously fickle nightcrawlers. By Jesse
McKinley.
