 This ``separate buy'' article is from Latin Trade magazine,
America's leading journal of Latin American business, finance and
trade: &HT;    THE `TEC': THE MIT OF LATIN AMERICA. The `Tec,' one of Latin
America's most wired universities, re-engineers learning.
 &HT;    Filed as BC-MEXICO:SUPER-WIRED-UNIVERSITY-LATINTRADE-NYTSF in
``f'' financial.
