<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-26 21:02 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7138 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a BC-NY-COUNTERFEIT-MONEY-     05-26 0547
